org.apache.polygene.spi.entity

Interface NamedAssociationState

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultNamedAssociationState, JSONNamedAssociationState

    public interface NamedAssociationState
extends Iterable<String>
    State holder for NamedAssociations. The actual state can be eager-loaded or lazy-loaded. This is an implementation detail. The Iterable<String> returns the names in the association set.
